Content: [dscrd-hush] <Privatoshi> What we didn't understand earlier this week, is that when you post screenshots to discord, they lose their compression. And whatever changes you made, become invalid.

Author: Gateway#3763
Content: [dscrd-hush] <Privatoshi> Google Play would not accept our screenshots for a week, it said they were invalid.

Author: Gateway#3763
Content: [dscrd-hush] <Privatoshi> So I posted in XDA discord, asking for assistance. Because they are really good with media and androids.

Author: Gateway#3763
Content: [dscrd-hush] <Privatoshi> Within 20 minutes of sending the screenshots over to  @BigLez, they were all sent back and finished, in a zip file. And they worked.

Author: Gateway#3763
Content: [dscrd-hush] <Privatoshi> I had no idea that they'd lose their format, if we sent them to someone else, in discord.
